{"word":"ἀνάδαστος","slug":"ἀνάδαστος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνάδαστος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀναδατέομαι'><el>ἀναδατέομαι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>divided anew, re-distributed</i>, <el>ἀν. γῆν ποιεῖν</el> (<a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <el>ἀναδασμός</el>) <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><el>ἀν. ποιεῖν τι</el> <i>to rescind</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b> <p/></div>"}]}